  <description>Plants 30–90 cm. Stems glabrous to sparsely tomentose. Leaves: blades linear to oblong, 10–30 cm, spinose-dentate to shallowly pinnatifid, main spines mostly 5–10 mm, abaxial faces glabrous or nearly so. Heads 1–10. Involucres 3–4 × 3–6 cm, glabrous. Phyllaries: outer and middle bodies densely scabridulous, marginal spinules 0.1–0.5 mm. Corollas purple. 2n = 32, 33, 34, 35.</description>
